text.tspan: Session 27: USB-only power, all 7 LEDs shown
A3 ← CV IN, A4 ← TRIG IN
1kΩ (white LED current limit), 330Ω (RGB LED current limit)
Diodes: BAT85 Schottky (30V 200mA, input clamps - see individual schematics)
Inputs: D4 (CV IN white), D11/D23/D24 (TRIG IN RGB)
Outputs: D12 (CV OUT white), A0/A1/A2 (TRIG OUT RGB), D25 (CC OUT white)
MIDI: CAN_TX (MIDI OUT white), A5 (MIDI IN white)
• Power: USB-C only (no battery) - see POWER_DISTRIBUTION.svg
• Input protection: BAT85 diodes + voltage dividers - see TOP_PCB_*.svg
• OLED FeatherWing: Stacked on M4 (I2C 0x3C, buttons D5/D6/D9)
